<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="298" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,500,2003]" pageId="1" pageNumber="298">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,338,1724,1750]" pageId="1" pageNumber="298">Etymology:</emphasis>
From Latin “ 
<emphasis box="[488,597,1725,1750]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="298">continuus</emphasis>
” (uninterrupted), in reference to the two uninterrupted elytral bands, one of the differential characters to separate the new taxon from the other three similar species.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,500,2003]" pageId="1" pageNumber="298">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,262,1796,1822]" pageId="1" pageNumber="298">Note.</emphasis>
The recently described species 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Portela &amp; Mermudes" authorityYear="2014" box="[626,808,1796,1823]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Conognatha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="298" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="coffeatus" subGenus="Pithiscus">
<emphasis box="[626,651,1796,1822]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="298">C.</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[669,690,1797,1822]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="298">P.</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[707,808,1796,1822]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="298">coffeatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Portela &amp; Mermudes" authorityYear="2014" box="[865,1005,1796,1823]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Conognatha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="298" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="puris" subGenus="Pithiscus">
<emphasis box="[865,891,1796,1822]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="298">C.</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[909,930,1797,1822]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="298">P.</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[947,1005,1797,1822]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="298">puris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are known only from their 
